          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "What if I need to cancel or change my order?",
            "answer": "<p>All orders placed on MotleyUSA.com are processed quickly. We will do our best to accommodate your requests. The fastest way to do this is to contact us is by emailing: Support@MotleyUSA.com or call<a href=\"tel:+18882731664\">1-888-273-1664</a>. When emailing please put “Change Order” in the subject line.</p>"
