          "settings": {
            "title": "What is your Return & Warranty Policy?",
            "answer": "<p>Motley products are made with the best engineering and materials available. All Motley frames are guaranteed against fault in manufacturing materials and workmanship. If your frames are damaged as a result of a manufacturing defect, we will gladly replace them at no extra charge. If the damage is not because of a manufacturing defect, please contact us at: Support@MotleyUSA.com, Motley will offer a replacement of the same or similar style at a reasonable charge.<br/><br/>ALL AUTHORIZED DEALERS (retail stores) will direct you to our website and our Customer Service Department. <br/><br/>IMPORTANT: Motley DOES NOT REPLACE OR WARRANTY SCRATCHED LENSES.</p>"
